topic: Movie Workflow Series ("Film Genre and directors explorative search")

goals.3: Identify the BGP for film genre
goals.4: Find how many western films are been released in each european country from 2010-01-01 to 2015-31-12 (the result set must be country IRI, label and #films).
goals.5: Consider only films directed by Woody Allen or Quentin Tarantino. Then consider the date of publication of these films (take the first one if there are more than one date of publication). Return the year with more films release for the two director (the result set must be two elements and for each element there must be present the director IRI, the label of the IRI, the year and the number of films).
goals.6: Identify the BGP for Academy Awards
goals.7: Consider films directed by Woody Allen or Quentin Tarantino separately. Return the film which won more Academy Awards for the two directors (the result set must be two elements - one related to Allen and the other related to Tarantino -  and for each element there must be present the director IRI with its label, the film IRI with its label and the number of Academy awards won).
goals.8: Consider the set of films directed by Allen or Tarantino. Return for each Academy Award the total number of nomination of these films (the result set must be a list of triples Academy Award IRI, label and #nomination).
